extends layout

block content
  section.page-hero.comments-hero
    p.eyebrow Community board
    h1 Comments
    p Drop a quick review, favorite order, or note for Downtown Donuts.

  section.comments-layout
    form.comment-form(action="#", method="post")
      h2 Post a Comment
      p.form-intro Keep it short, helpful, and real.

      div.form-group
        label(for="name") Name
        input#name(type="text", name="name", maxlength="60", placeholder="Your name")

      div.form-group
        label(for="comment") Comment
        textarea#comment(name="comment", maxlength="500", rows="5", placeholder="What should people know?")

      p.form-note Database connection will be added in the full-stack step.
      button.button.primary(type="submit") Post Comment

    section.comment-feed(aria-label="Customer comments")
      div.feed-header
        h2 Recent Posts
        p Real customer notes will show here.

      article.comment-card
        div.comment-meta
          strong Alex
          span Just now
        p Solid coffee, quick service, and the maple bar is worth grabbing.

      article.comment-card
        div.comment-meta
          strong Jordan
          span Yesterday
        p Clean menu page and easy order links. Good spot for a quick downtown stop.

      article.comment-card
        div.comment-meta
          strong Casey
          span 2 days ago
        p Simple, fresh, and easy to use on mobile.

      button.button.secondary(type="button") Load More